          <zone forceUpdate='true' h='9765' id='16' type-v2='text' w='98828' x='586' y='1042'>
            <formatted-text>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#ffffff' fontsize='18'>San Jose 311 | </run>
              <run fontcolor='#ffffff' fontsize='18'>Response Time Analysis </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#d9e2ec'>Click any category or quarter to filter. Streetlight outages are the citywide bottleneck; weekend submissions take ~3x longer to resolve.</run>
            </formatted-text>
            <zone-style>
              <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
              <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
              <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
              <format attr='margin' value='4' />
              <format attr='padding-top' value='8' />
              <format attr='padding-bottom' value='8' />
              <format attr='padding-left' value='12' />
              <format attr='background-color' value='#26547c' />
            </zone-style>
          </zone>
          <zone forceUpdate='true' h='46814' id='17' type-v2='text' w='34835' x='64579' y='52144'>
            <formatted-text>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#6e6c68' fontsize='11'>Key findings</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#6e6c68'>• Streetlight outages are the citywide bottleneck — median ~800+ hours to close, slow in every district.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#6e6c68'>• Weekend submissions take ~3x longer to resolve, controlling for category and season.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#6e6c68'>• Demand concentrates downtown (District 3), but controlling for request mix, Districts 1, 6 &amp; 10 are the slowest to get resolution.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#6e6c68' italic='true'>Map covers the ~43% of requests with usable GPS coordinates.</run>
            </formatted-text>
            <zone-style>
              <format attr='border-color' value='#d8d6d0' />
              <format attr='border-style' value='solid' />
              <format attr='border-width' value='1' />
              <format attr='margin' value='8' />
              <format attr='padding' value='8' />
              <format attr='background-color' value='#ffffff' />
            </zone-style>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
